room_title: Escape room "The Psych Ward" by Locked Away Escapes in Jonesboro
room_description: You are committed to a mental institution by your loved ones. You are not crazy. You just chose the wrong enemy, Anna, a deceitful menacing woman who hides under a false veil of charitable innocence. She plots murder and needs you out of the way before you blow her cover. Your warnings about Anna fall on deaf ears, and in turn, you are committed. Will you find the way out of your cell and expose Anna, or will you forever be in solitary confinement?
